item.title: Loading mopar
item.dc:creator: @Nazgand Nazgand
item.description:
@Nazgand wrote:

I’m pretty sure that is an out of memory error.

Solution 1:
Try “Download Without Cache”, since you already have the cache, and try using the new shortcuts the install makes, as they allow Moparscape to use up to 500MB Maximum.
http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,82778.0.html

Solution 2: I
f that doesn’t work, then you have to many programs running. I suggest for that you Download “Spybot Search & Destroy”, scan your computer, delete all the bad stuff it finds, and delete all the startup entries except those listed as “SYSTEM.INI”. Then restart.
